    *   **Sourcing:** Thrift stores, consignment shops, online marketplaces [ultimatethrifting](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-11) [medium](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-1) [vendoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-5) [salehoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-6) [fitsmallbusiness](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0].     *   **Selling Price:** Y2K vintage sells well on Depop and Poshmark, with average prices between $25-$45. 90s Vintage also sells well on Depop and eBay, with prices between $35-$55 [shelftrend](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/2-0).

*   **Vintage Clothing and Accessories:** Look for items at least 20 years old [vendoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-5). Margins can be high, potentially reaching 100% or more [salehoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-6].
    *   **Sourcing:** Thrift stores, estate sales, online marketplaces [ultimatethrifting](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-11) [medium](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-1) [vendoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-5) [salehoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-6) [fitsmallbusiness](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0].

    *   **Platforms:** Depop, Poshmark, Etsy [salehoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-6).
*   **Designer Items (Handbags):** Rare bags from brands like Hermes and Chanel can yield significant profits [salehoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-6]. Handbags can have margins of 40–70% [vendoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/2-2).
    *   **Sourcing:** Consignment boutiques, estate sales, online marketplaces [spocket](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-7).
    *   **Selling Price:** Depends on the brand, rarity, and condition.
    *   **Platforms:** TheRealReal, Vestiaire Collective [salehoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-6) [lifehacker](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-13) [vendoo](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-4].
        *   **Authentication:** The RealReal is the only resale company that authenticates every single item they sell [therealreal](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/4-10]. *   **Depop:** Suited for vintage and streetwear [nifty](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-2) [amzscout](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-6) [lifehacker](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-13) [youtube](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/1-8).
